		<category term="News" />
	</entry>
	<entry>
		<title>Our Elective Convention Was The Best Ever - Adamu</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="/index.php/events/97-our-elective-convention-was-the-best-ever-adamu"/>
		<published>2022-08-30T12:22:00+00:00</published>
		<updated>2022-08-30T12:22:00+00:00</updated>
		<id>/index.php/events/97-our-elective-convention-was-the-best-ever-adamu</id>
		<author>
			<name>Super User</name>
			<email>tunde.obadina@afbis.com</email>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;feed-description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The National Chairman of the All Progressive Congress (APC), Senator (Dr.) Abdullahi Adamu (CON) Turakin Keffi, has commended the organization of the last special elective convention of the Party. Adamu stated this while receiving the report of the media and publicity committee of the convention at the national secretariat of the party.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;feed-description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The National Chairman of the All Progressive Congress (APC), Senator (Dr.) Abdullahi Adamu (CON) Turakin Keffi, has commended the organization of the last special elective convention of the Party. Adamu stated this while receiving the report of the media and publicity committee of the convention at the national secretariat of the party.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</content>
